    <bpmn2:dataObject id="dataObject_iq4agg" imixs:datatype="prompt-data" name="Prompt">
      <bpmn2:documentation id="documentation_fFWo7Q"><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<PromptDefinition>
    <prompt_options>{"n_predict": 2096, "temperature": 0.3, "top_p": 0.9}</prompt_options>
    <prompt role="user"><![CDATA[
# Current Task: Create a new Offer for the customer based on the preselected product list.


## Customer Request: 

Firstname: <itemvalue>customer.firstname</itemvalue>
Lastname: <itemvalue>customer.lastname</itemvalue>
E-Mail: <itemvalue>customer.email</itemvalue>

<itemvalue>request.description</itemvalue>

## Product Selection

The following products are relevant for the current request:

<for-each-ref item="product.ref">
Product: <itemvalue>product.name</itemvalue>
Category: <itemvalue>product.category</itemvalue> / <itemvalue>product.subcategory</itemvalue>
Price: <itemvalue>product.price</itemvalue> <itemvalue>_currency</itemvalue>
Product Details: 
<itemvalue>product.description</itemvalue>

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
</for-each-ref>

]]]]><![CDATA[>
</prompt>
<loglevel>FINE</loglevel>
</PromptDefinition>    ]]></bpmn2:documentation>
    </bpmn2:dataObject>
    <bpmn2:dataObject id="dataObject_u4ZytA" imixs:datatype="form-data" name="Offer Form">
      <bpmn2:documentation id="documentation_lSiw2w"><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0"?>
<imixs-form>
  <imixs-form-section columns="1" label="E-Mail Summary" readonly="true" >
    <item name="customer.summary" type="custom" path="markdown" />
  </imixs-form-section>

  <imixs-form-section columns="2" label="Master Data">
    <item name="customer.ref" 
      type="custom"  required="false"
      path="workitemlink"
      options="($workflowgroup:Product)((type:workitem) OR (type:workitemarchive))"
      label="Customer:" />   

   <item name="product.ref" 
      type="custom"  required="true"
      path="workitemlink"
      options="($workflowgroup:Product)((type:workitem) OR (type:workitemarchive))"
      label="Product Suggestions:" />

  </imixs-form-section>


  <imixs-form-section columns="1" label="Offer Proposal:" readonly="false" >
    <item name="offer.proposal" type="custom" path="markdowneditor" />
  </imixs-form-section>

  
  


</imixs-form>
]]></bpmn2:documentation>
      <bpmn2:dataState id="dataState_X4nVjg"/>
    </bpmn2:dataObject>
    <bpmn2:association id="association_0SKl0g" sourceRef="dataObject_u4ZytA" targetRef="Task_3">
      <bpmn2:documentation id="documentation_VQTg6w"/>
    </bpmn2:association>
    <bpmn2:dataObject id="dataObject_g68BvQ" imixs:datatype="prompt-data" name="Prompt">
      <bpmn2:documentation id="documentation_0KRD6g"><![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<PromptDefinition>
    <prompt_options>{"n_predict": 4096, "temperature": 0}</prompt_options>
    <prompt role="system"><![CDATA[You are a sales representative of the 'DYNAMIXS.AI GmbH'. Your task is to respond to incoming inquiries and provide suggestions for offers.

# Instructions for creating the offer:

1. Politely thank the customer for the inquiry and briefly address the customer's concern in the introduction. Show your interest in the customer's project.
2. Choose the most suitable products for the request.
3. **Do not include more than one product per category.** If multiple products are from the same category, pick the one that best fits the request.
4. Create a clear table with the following columns:
   - Product
   - Quantity
   - Price per unit
5. Provide a short, customer-friendly explanation of why each selected product was chosen. 
7. **Focus exclusively on the selected products.** Do not justify exclusions or mention unselected products in any way.
7. Ensure the table contains only the selected products (one per category).
8. The offer and all explanations should be written in English.


# Our Company 

DYNAMIXS.AI GmbH
Frei-Otto-Str. 4
D-80797 München#

## Contact Sales Assistant: 
Ralph Soika 
E-Mail: ralph.soika@imixs.com
Phone : 089 45213616
]]]]><![CDATA[>
</prompt>
</PromptDefinition>    ]]></bpmn2:documentation>
    </bpmn2:dataObject>
