      <bpmn2:documentation id="documentation_92A4gw"><![CDATA[<PromptDefinition>
 <prompt_options>{"n_predict": 2048, "temperature": 0.2, "top_p": 0.9}</prompt_options>
 <prompt role="system"><![CDATA[ 
  You are a process analyst. A workflow has just been completed. 
  Create a brief project insight: 
  What specifically happened? (Include relevant names from people, companies, products when mentioned.)
   - Is there anything unusual or important to remember for the future? (Pay attention to user comments - they often contain important warnings or decisions.)
  No general advice. Only project-specific facts and insights. ]]]]><![CDATA[>
  </prompt> 
  <prompt role="user"><![CDATA[
     {chronicle}
    ]]]]><![CDATA[> 
  </prompt> 
</PromptDefinition>]]></bpmn2:documentation>
    </bpmn2:dataObject>
